1. ping gcr.io to make sure that google images is accessible.
2. change init_node.sh accordingly.
3. make sure that hostnames are correctly mapped.
4. execute init_node.sh on master.
5. execute init_master.sh to init master.
6. execute init_node.sh on every node.
7. join master on the nodes.
8. set up network.
9. set up dashboard.
10. set up monitor  